data.description: Gorgeous Home Ready to Sell! This upgraded gem features a well-maintained exterior and a modern, spacious interior. With plenty of roomy bedrooms and a stunning backyard, it's the perfect place for anyone seeking a dream home. Step inside the airy living room, basked in natural light and a refreshing breeze. The gleaming laminated floors add a touch of elegance throughout the entire house. Stay cozy with three bedrooms, two baths and a den on cool evenings with the den's inviting gas fireplace. The stylish kitchen boasts white cabinets, a sleek glass backsplash, and granite countertops, complete with matching appliances. Upgraded central air conditioning system with energy-saving solar panels and a water softener system not only enhances the value of the property but also promotes eco-friendly living.  Outdoors, nature enthusiasts will adore the expansive backyard, ideal for hosting gatherings, entertaining guests, and firing up the BBQ. The sprawling grassy lawn is a haven for children, while offering the potential to build an ADU or a pool for summertime fun.
